  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/43749a3e0fee7a716c0a63bdaf7baa89.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/43749a3e0fee7a716c0a63bdaf7baa89.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/43749a3e0fee7a716c0a63bdaf7baa89.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CASE is a <strong>turn-based strategy</strong> game that can be played with up to 8 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main objective is to ally with one other player and eliminate all enemies from the map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start the game with a chosen tile and complete your base on the map during the peace phase.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can place pickaxes and shields on your tiles for production and defense, which can be upgraded up to 3 levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/14634b0bdf3d9ebd2dbbe51dad5be8b4.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/14634b0bdf3d9ebd2dbbe51dad5be8b4.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/14634b0bdf3d9ebd2dbbe51dad5be8b4.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you expand across the map, you have a chance to find various unique cards; using these cards strategically is entirely up to you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Development cards</strong> help you grow faster.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/58218afd87602a74e547e603d0b60327.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/58218afd87602a74e547e603d0b60327.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/58218afd87602a74e547e603d0b60327.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Attack cards</strong> allow you to fight against your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/5d61f7e653b0461695272fe0d20d7dbb.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/5d61f7e653b0461695272fe0d20d7dbb.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/5d61f7e653b0461695272fe0d20d7dbb.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trap cards</strong> catch enemies by surprise if they try to conquer you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/edaed920a43cb786343f7b9edbc3b8cf.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/edaed920a43cb786343f7b9edbc3b8cf.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/edaed920a43cb786343f7b9edbc3b8cf.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Political cards</strong> give you the power to interfere with other players' strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/69c201f3ab71902448ab66e6dd097783.poster.avif?t=1733400118\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/69c201f3ab71902448ab66e6dd097783.webm?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098580/extras/69c201f3ab71902448ab66e6dd097783.mp4?t=1733400118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, in CASE, nothing is bad if you're winning in the end. Join the battlefield and fight against your enemies!</p></li></ul>",
